            <title xml:id="name261-2" xml:lang="fr-x-bhsyre" source="#bib261-1">Šāḇōr w-ʾĪsḥāq w-Maʿnā w-ʾAḇrōhōm w-Šemʿōn</title>
            <title xml:id="name261-3" xml:lang="fr" source="#bib261-1">Shahpour, Isaac, Ma‘na, Abraham et Simon (texte)</title>
            <title xml:id="name261-4"
                   xml:lang="en"
                   source="#bib261-1"
                   syriaca-tags="#syriaca-headword">Shabōr, Isaac, Ma‘na, Abraham and Simon (text)</title>
            <note xml:lang="syr" type="incipit" source="#bib261-1">
               <quote>ܒܫܢܬ ܬܠܬܝܢ ܕܡܠܟܘܬܗ ܕܫܒܘܪ ܡܠܟܐ ܕܦܪܣ: ܩܪܒܘ ܓܒܪ̈ܐ ܡܓܘ̈ܫܐ: ܘܐܟܠܘ ܩܪ̈ܨܝܗܘܢ ܕܢܨܪ̈ܝܐ.</quote>
            </note>
            <note xml:lang="fr" type="incipit" source="#bib261-1">
               <quote>En la trentième année du règne de Shahpour roi de Perse, les Mages vinrent calomnier les chrétiens.</quote>
            </note>
            <note xml:lang="syr" type="explicit" source="#bib261-1">
               <quote>ܘܦܩܕ ܠܩܫܬ̈ܐ: ܘܡܚܐܘܗܝ ܒܓܐܪ̈ܐ ܘܡܝܬ. ܘܐܬܘ ܐܢܫܐ ܐܚ̈ܐ ܟܪ̈ܣܛܝܢܐ ܘܓܢܒܘ ܫܠܕܝ̈ܗܘܢ: ܘܩܒܪܘ ܡܛܫܝܐܝܬ.</quote>
            </note>
            <note xml:lang="fr" type="explicit" source="#bib261-1">
               <quote>Et il commanda les archers et ils tirèrent des flèches et il mourut. Et des frères chrétiens vinrent dérober leurs corps et les ensevelirent en cachette.</quote>
            </note>
            <note type="editions">
               <bibl source="#bib261-1">
                  <author>(1) Bedjan, P.</author>
                  <title>(1) AMS 2</title>
                  <citedRange>(1) p. 51-56</citedRange>
               </bibl>
            </note>
            <note type="editions">
               <bibl source="#bib261-1">
                  <author>(2) Assemani, S. E.</author>
                  <title>(2) ASMOO 1</title>
                  <citedRange>(2) p. 226-229</citedRange>
               </bibl>
            </note>
            <note type="editions">
               <bibl source="#bib261-1">
                  <author>(3) Peeters, P.</author>
                  <title>(3) AS Novembris, t. IV</title>
                  <citedRange>(3) Bruxelles, 1925, p. 428-432</citedRange>
               </bibl>
            </note>
